/** \page parameters Parameters

This page is a list of all user parameters in PRISMS-PF. Here, we document them in tables
organized by subsection with names, default values, acceptable values (patterns),
descriptions, and aliases.

Subsections that end in 0 are number in the parameter file. You can as many of these as
you would like. By default you have `Numbers::default_subsections`. To change have many
subsections you have, you can write something like the following.
@code{.cpp}
UserInputParameters<dim>(cli_options.get_parameters_filename(), 10);
@endcode

@note You can copy parameter names to clipboard by clicking on them!

@parameter_list

*/
